---
title: Gnocchi Bolognese with Fresh Tomato Sauce, Carrots and Parmesan
description: Gnocchi are pillowy potato dumplings that are delicious when doused with fresh tomato sauce. We're taking gnocchi a step further by pan-frying them until they're crispy and golden-brown and then tossing in a rich tomato sauce. If you thought gnocchi was irresistible before, wait until you taste this recipe.
